  "detailed_description": "Son of Aral is a 3D Tower defense/Sandbox game.<br><br>You're lock inside a fake sky and an island under your feet,you have to destroy the enemy's portal with turrets to expand this island,when the island is big enough and happy, it will give you the key to get out in return.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1357890/extras/7591eb54d64365a29ec9dba6ac60d6c2.poster.avif?t=1712802546\" width=428 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1357890/extras/7591eb54d64365a29ec9dba6ac60d6c2.webm?t=1712802546\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1357890/extras/7591eb54d64365a29ec9dba6ac60d6c2.mp4?t=1712802546\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Core Gameplays:<br>Collect: chop trees, mine stones and ores.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1357890/extras/e9002e52f16aa8233c13dc512edcaf2a.poster.avif?t=1712802546\" width=346 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1357890/extras/e9002e52f16aa8233c13dc512edcaf2a.webm?t=1712802546\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1357890/extras/e9002e52f16aa8233c13dc512edcaf2a.mp4?t=1712802546\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Craft: build furnace, turrets, walls, tools, new technology and all kinds of other items.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1357890/extras/13dac3cc597ddba76300bc6875bd53c8.poster.avif?t=1712802546\" width=400 height=176 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1357890/extras/13dac3cc597ddba76300bc6875bd53c8.webm?t=1712802546\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1357890/extras/13dac3cc597ddba76300bc6875bd53c8.mp4?t=1712802546\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Survival: protect the island's core, plant seeds and water crop, cook with furnace.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1357890/extras/2a9e5faca59eced43428f4d763b419c3.poster.avif?t=1712802546\" width=656 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1357890/extras/2a9e5faca59eced43428f4d763b419c3.webm?t=1712802546\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1357890/extras/2a9e5faca59eced43428f4d763b419c3.mp4?t=1712802546\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Tower defence: build turrets to defend enemies, block enemy's path by putting walls, upgrade your technology to unlock better turrets.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1357890/extras/a13727e3379f5b0ec0fbc1623d75eed2.poster.avif?t=1712802546\" width=754 height=422 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1357890/extras/a13727e3379f5b0ec0fbc1623d75eed2.webm?t=1712802546\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1357890/extras/a13727e3379f5b0ec0fbc1623d75eed2.mp4?t=1712802546\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Choosing Character:<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.co